data.actual_result: The values reset themselves which shouldn't happen because you haven't yet left the settings.
data.short_description: making any changes to the bitrate and user limit values in a voice channel and clicking on permissions and then clicking back resets your changes.
data.steps_to_repro: - Create a server. - Long press on the general voice channel. - Click on edit channel. - Make changes to the bitrate and/or the user limit values (do not save them). - Scroll down and click on permissions. - Click on back. - Observe the bitrate and user limit values.
